Package common

Class ParkingReport

java.lang.Object
common.ParkingReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ParkingReport extends Object implements Serializable
A simple data holder for parking-related statistics, typically used in generating summary reports. Contains aggregated data such as total parking entries, number of extensions, number of late departures, and duration distribution (less than 4 hours, between 4 to 8 hours, and more than 8 hours).

      public ParkingReport(int totalEntries, int totalExtends, int totalLates, int lessThanFour, int betweenFourToEight, int moreThanEight)
      Creates a new ParkingReport with all the needed statistics.
      Parameters:
      totalEntries - Total number of parking events that happened
      totalExtends - Number of sessions where users extended their parking time
      totalLates - Number of sessions that ended after the allowed time
      lessThanFour - Number of parkings that lasted less than 4 hours
      betweenFourToEight - Number of parkings that lasted between 4 to 8 hours
      moreThanEight - Number of parkings that lasted more than 8 hours
